Marrying the delectable mysteries of the Orient with a classic Italian touch this luxury scent brings together all the elements fit for the ideal woman. Giorgio Armani Idole Dâ is a magnificent tribute to the breathtaking woman who personifies charm and grace. Created by Bruno Jovanovic thisÂ Eau de Parfum is made for the celebrated house of Armani.

Citrus notes of bitter orange extracts of juicy pear spicy hints of ginger and aromatic davana make up a refreshing top note. This flows into a fragrant heart note composed of the sweet scent of rose loukoum exotic hints of jasmine and the seductive aroma of saffron.
